NORTHERN CAPE - Entrepreneur Mpho Cornelius is living her dream of running a cafe and African spa that showcases her traditional life while helping her community.After living in Johannesburg, the young woman decided to return to her home town of Kuruman in the Northern Cape and start a small business.The Workshop ko Kasi is gaining momentum, and is getting much-welcomed exposure at the Tourism Indaba currently under way in Durban. eNCA